16:01.670 --> 16:03.627
But I really was trying.

16:04.790 --> 16:08.909
Hmm.

16:08.960 --> 16:10.371
What you looking for?

16:10.420 --> 16:14.505
Uh, I am I-looking
for these thingies...

16:14.550 --> 16:15.631
