catheters.

16:17.060 --> 16:18.767
Yeah.

16:20.730 --> 16:22.220
What the hell was that?

16:22.270 --> 16:23.726
Did I just giggle
and flip my hair at him?

16:23.770 --> 16:25.147
I can't giggle-flip him.

16:25.190 --> 16:26.680
