to eat dinner tonight.

17:08.359 --> 17:10.101
Now I can do it with you.

17:11.480 --> 17:13.608
Eat dinner, not do it...

17:13.650 --> 17:15.196
unless --
unless dinner goes well.

17:15.240 --> 17:16.355
Then all bets are off.

17:19.410 --> 17:20.444
See ya later.

17:20.490 --> 17:22.948
Bye.

17:23.000 --> 17:25.458
