want to eat dinner,

17:38.300 --> 17:39.847
and then they'll be up
half the night.

17:39.890 --> 17:40.755
Oh, don't worry.

17:40.810 --> 17:41.925
If they want to stay up

17:41.970 --> 17:43.472
a little bit
past their bedtime,

17:43.520 --> 17:44.726
I'll be up.

17:44.770 --> 17:46.477
Hey, kids!

17:48.770 --> 17:49.896
Okay.

17:49.940 --> 17:51.260
Since she got here,

17:51.320 --> 17:53.027
we have not been alone
long enough to have sex,

17:53.070 --> 17:54.686
