18:46.750 --> 18:48.036
Well --

18:48.080 --> 18:49.491
Stella. Hey.

18:49.540 --> 18:51.781
Seriously, dude, that was
not your cue to appear.

18:52.630 --> 18:53.995
Did I say that out loud?

18:54.050 --> 18:55.165
Yeah.

18:55.210 --> 18:56.120
You sure you're okay?

18:56.170 --> 18:57.547
Mm-hmm.

18:57.590 --> 18:59.467
I thought she was having
a stroke the other day.

19:00.800 --> 19:03.007
And you --
you must be Wes, right?

19:03.050 --> 19:04.347
I'm Will Grant.

19:04.390 --> 19:05.801
Stella talks about you
all the time.

19:05.850 --> 19:07.227
Oh. Really?

19:07.270 --> 19:08.681
She -- She hasn't
mentioned you before.

19:08.730 --> 19:09.970
Yes, I have.

19:10.020 --> 19:11.340
This is
Sadie's new doctor.

19:11.400 --> 19:13.141
Oh!

19:13.190 --> 19:16.023
Sorry, I thought you'd have
a different sort of face.

19:17.690 --> 19:19.101
What -- What kind of face did
you think I was gonna have?

19:19.150 --> 19:22.370
Just, um, older,
more doctor-y.

19:22.410 --> 19:24.367
Yeah.
Dr. Chang: Hey, Wes!

19:24.410 --> 19:26.117
Oh.

19:26.160 --> 19:27.571
But I guess young
and attractive doctors

19:27.620 --> 19:28.997
