21:11.560 --> 21:13.221
Oh.
What?

21:13.270 --> 21:14.226
I--

21:14.270 --> 21:15.806
There must be
some mistake.

21:19.020 --> 21:20.602
Man: You have the right
to remain silent.

21:20.650 --> 21:22.027
Anything you say can and will
be used against you

21:22.070 --> 21:23.026
in a court of law.

21:31.580 --> 21:32.900
How could you do this?

21:32.950 --> 21:35.032
I stuck my neck out
to get you that job,

21:35.080 --> 21:36.662
and this is
how you repay me?

21:36.710 --> 21:37.996
Okay, Stella,
I think you're blowing it

21:38.040 --> 21:39.496
a little bit
out of proportion.

21:39.540 --> 21:41.417
