proportion? Stella.

21:41.460 --> 21:43.508
Aiden, you broke the law.
Barely.

21:43.550 --> 21:45.291
They prescribe those pills
to kids.

21:45.340 --> 21:46.922
Every college student
has them.

21:46.970 --> 21:49.348
All T did was sell some
to some responsible adults

21:49.390 --> 21:51.097
that actually needed them.

21:51.140 --> 21:52.460
Do you have any idea what
those soccer moms go through?

21:52.520 --> 21:53.726
It's terrible.

21:53.770 --> 21:54.760
You know what?

21:54.810 --> 21:56.517
I'm done with you.

22:00.610 --> 22:02.021
It's kind of hard
to be done with me

22:02.070 --> 22:03.276
when we're both stuck
in here.

22:03.320 --> 22:05.482
Stella Abbott.

22:07.950 --> 22:09.190
Free to go.

22:09.240 --> 22:10.480
Thank you.

