22:23.710 --> 22:25.337
So you stay.

22:25.380 --> 22:26.506
Wait.
I can't just leave him.

22:26.550 --> 22:28.370
Not really up to you.

22:29.590 --> 22:32.343
Aiden, I'm gonna get you
out of here.

22:32.390 --> 22:34.301
I thought
you're done with me?

22:34.350 --> 22:36.307
I am.

22:36.350 --> 22:37.727
But we're still family.

