You have to bail him out.

25:07.340 --> 25:08.660
Your brother needs to face

25:08.710 --> 25:10.667
the consequences
of his actions.

25:10.710 --> 25:12.792
It's the only way
he'll ever learn.

25:12.840 --> 25:14.330
I can't believe
you're being so cold.

25:14.380 --> 25:16.587
Oh, he's gonna be okay.

25:16.640 --> 25:18.847
I spoke to a law-professor
friend of mine.

25:18.890 --> 25:20.767
She says,
as a first-time offender,

25:20.810 --> 25:22.801
